import React from 'react'

import { DuoHeatmap, Row } from 'duo-heatmap'
import 'duo-heatmap/dist/index.css'

const rows: Row[] = [
  { label: 'Monday', data: [] },
  { label: 'Tuesday', data: [] },
  { label: 'Wednesday', data: [] },
  { label: 'Thursday', data: [] },
  { label: 'Friday', data: [] },
  { label: 'Saturday', data: [] },
  { label: 'Sunday', data: [] }
]

const App = () => {
  return <DuoHeatmap rows={rows} color1='#fff' color2='#000' />
}

export default App
